{"tid":1131476,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lisa不斷跟他揮手…當場哭了！","createTime":"2019-04-29T16:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T03:12:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":224,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd3512ae063d8598f1fa02bac0e50454c12d7e8","tid":1131476,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"南韓大勢女團BLACKPINK近日忙於全球巡演，她們28日抵達哈密爾頓站，就在演唱會尾聲時，Lisa瞄見台下有名粉絲眼睛雖然失明，卻依舊拍著手享受演唱會，令她當場飆出眼淚、摀嘴巴，而發現她不對勁的成員Jennie、Ros&eacute;紛紛上前查看，台上、台下的氣氛令人動容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4060/d4060393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4060%2Fd4060393.jpg&h=275bfd88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/93f8d29dly1g2jxzdytpug20dc07mqv8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F93f8d29dly1g2jxzdytpug20dc07mqv8.gif&h=ba36ccf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa發現台下有粉絲眼睛看不見，依舊暖心與對方揮手。（圖／翻攝自supahnerd推特）<br />\n<br />\n根據推特帳號為「supahnerd」所釋出的影片，該名網友目睹Lisa站在台上揮手打招呼時，發現有位眼睛看不見的粉絲站在其中，她秒紅眼眶、轉身擦淚，爾後Jennie看見她的擦淚動作，立刻彎腰詢問，Ros&eacute;也從遠方走到她身邊給予擁抱安慰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4060/d4060396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4060%2Fd4060396.jpg&h=6fbbf3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/93f8d29dly1g2jxzlx41ag20dm07shdw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F93f8d29dly1g2jxzlx41ag20dm07shdw.gif&h=0494a477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼網友「supahnerd」敘述Lisa發現台下有粉絲眼睛看不見，暖心的舉動。（圖／翻攝自supahnerd推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4060/d4060395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4060%2Fd4060395.jpg&h=e134f40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/93f8d29dly1g2jxzs7akng20hs0a0npd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F93f8d29dly1g2jxzs7akng20hs0a0npd.gif&h=85da37c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友「supahnerd」敘述，Lisa之所以停在他們面前揮手，正是因為她發現該名盲人粉絲，「當歌曲結束時，我喊了Lisa，並替該名男生（盲人粉絲）揮手回覆，Lisa揮手道再見、哭了，我後來告訴他，Lisa跟你說再見，他很開心，也很享受這個演唱會。」這段互動不只逼哭Lisa，粉絲也紛紛留下感動的眼淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4060/d4060390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4060%2Fd4060390.jpg&h=a9d4fa6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/93f8d29dly1g2jxz5fizvg20ga082u0z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F93f8d29dly1g2jxz5fizvg20ga082u0z.gif&h=4d254c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有網友挖出另一個角度的畫面，當時男粉絲很享受演唱會。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，後來有網友掀出另一個角度的畫面，當時該位盲人粉絲站在台下，雖然看不見台上的表演，依舊露出滿足的笑容，跟著音樂節奏拍手，這幕逼哭許多網友，也令粉絲感同身受為何Lisa會忍不住淚灑舞台，稱讚Lisa人美心善。"},{"pid":"96ccef92cc6fa24105e8ca10c4c594a0df051149","tid":1131476,"uid":531,"like":78,"dislike":141,"score":-63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"睇嚟條友除咗盲仲係聾嘅"},{"pid":"9234ff275045f7272f22ae94f6a9dd6a3523998a","tid":1131476,"uid":238483,"like":180,"dislike":32,"score":148,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"Blind"},{"pid":"3f0d67ae5dbde67e893fc7c0ca1d35d2ce41ed38","tid":1131476,"uid":89660,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"#無悔"},{"pid":"c92b899aa0d599e0c942739c24d0a0d289751afe","tid":1131476,"uid":74065,"like":24,"dislike":46,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"9234ff275045f7272f22ae94f6a9dd6a3523998a","tid":1131476,"uid":238483,"like":180,"dislike":32,"score":148,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"Blind"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"嘩你好口賤"},{"pid":"53d446e28b9833891fdea595789fe82eda6b9ccf","tid":1131476,"uid":238483,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"c92b899aa0d599e0c942739c24d0a0d289751afe","tid":1131476,"uid":74065,"like":24,"dislike":46,"sco